  <h1>Data Deletion Policy</h1>
  <p>This Data Deletion Policy applies to all users who interact with Agatha Virelle apps or services through Facebook or Instagram integration.</p>

  <h2>1. User-Initiated Deletion</h2>
  <p>If you wish to delete your data associated with our app, please contact us via email at <a href="mailto:agathavirelle@gmail.com">agathavirelle@gmail.com</a>. We will process your request within 7 business days.</p>

  <h2>2. Automatic Data Deletion</h2>
  <p>All user data retrieved via Facebook or Instagram APIs is automatically removed once access is revoked by the user or app is removed from your connected accounts.</p>

  <h2>3. What Data Is Deleted</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Instagram profile info</li>
    <li>Content publishing permissions</li>
    <li>Page insights, hashtag searches, or media analytics</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this policy or need help, contact us at: <a href="mailto:agathavirelle@gmail.com">agathavirelle@gmail.com</a></p>

  <p><em>Last updated: April 2025</em></p>
